overview:
Barbieri Orthodontics is one of the best orthodontic offices serving the greater Nashville, TN, area. Dr. Damon Barbieri and his staff employ state of the art technology to tailor treatments according to each individual patient’s needs. Dr. Barbieri prides himself on creating and maintaining the best smiles in Tennessee through an undying attention to detail and passion for excellence.

With two locations in Nashville and Smyrna, Tennessee, Barbieri Orthodontics uses state of the art technology combined with an individualized approach to Orthodontics to develop and maintain the brightest smiles in all of Tennessee. Dr. Damon Barbieri tailors each treatment to the individual according to their specific needs. Barbieri Orthodontics prides itself on developing the life-altering confidence that comes from wearing a perfect smile.

Services Offered: Braces, Clear Braces, Invisalign, TMJ/TMD Treatment, Children’s Braces, Teen Braces, Damon Braces

Brands Carried: Invisalign, Damon Braces Professional Associations: Middle Tennessee Society for Advanced Dentistry, The Progressive Orthodontist Study Club, Millennium Study Club, American Association of Orthodontists, Tennessee Dental Association, Nashville Dental Society
